### Closira API — smoke test requests
### Use with VS Code "REST Client" extension or convert to curl.

@host = http://localhost:8000

### 1. Health check
GET {{host}}/health

### 2. Create enquiry — pricing question
POST {{host}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Sarah M.",
  "customer_contact": "+91 98765 43210",
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "message": "Hi! What's the price for a 2BHK deep cleaning?"
}

### 3. Create enquiry — booking
POST {{host}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Rohan K.",
  "customer_contact": "rohan@example.com",
  "channel": "email",
  "message": "I want to book an appointment for Saturday morning."
}

### 4. Create enquiry — complaint (auto-escalates)
POST {{host}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Anita D.",
  "customer_contact": "+91 99887 11223",
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "message": "Very unhappy with the service. I want a refund and to speak to a manager."
}

### 5. Create enquiry — no SOP match (auto-escalates)
POST {{host}}/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Vikram R.",
  "channel": "call",
  "message": "Just calling to say hello."
}

### 6. List all enquiries
GET {{host}}/enquiry

### 7. List only escalated enquiries
GET {{host}}/enquiry?status=escalated

### 8. Get full conversation history (replace ID with one from step 2)
GET {{host}}/enquiry/enq_REPLACE/history

### 9. Schedule a follow-up
POST {{host}}/enquiry/enq_REPLACE/followup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delay_minutes": 60,
  "message_template": "Hi Sarah, just checking in — happy to share more details."
}

### 10. Escalate an enquiry manually
POST {{host}}/enquiry/enq_REPLACE/escalate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer requested manager after pricing discussion.",
  "urgency": "high"
}

### 11. List follow-ups
GET {{host}}/follow-ups

### 12. Dashboard stats
GET {{host}}/stats

### 13. Resolve enquiry
POST {{host}}/enquiry/enq_REPLACE/resolve
